                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9789" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1469</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">734 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘三姐数字人：穿越时空之旅，传统融现代的数智创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Liu Sanjie Digital Human: A Time-Transcending Journey, an Innovative Chapter of Tradition Meets Modernity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡明明，陈聪聪，刘民坤，魏泽林</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西旅发一键游数字文旅产业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘三姐数字人；文化传承；数字化创新；科技赋能</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Liu Sanjie Digital Human; Cultural Heritage; Digital Innovation; Technology Empowerment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人工智能时代的到来和元宇宙概念的爆发，使虚拟数字人成为未来传播的重要带动点和关键引爆点。本案例以广西文旅厅与旅游发展集团打造的“刘三姐数字人”为例，探讨传统文化与科技融合的数字化转型路径。项目通过虚拟数字人技术，重塑国家级非遗“刘三姐”形象，构建集智能导览、文化讲解、互动服务于一体的文旅推广新模式。案例深度应用数字文化IP理论，通过IP形象现代化设计，多维内容生态，强化文化符号辨识度；依托营销变革理论，突破传统同质化模式，以虚实融合的7&#215;24小时智能服务、数据驱动的个性化推荐重构用户触达路径；结合情感营销理论，通过山歌文化共鸣、用户共创社群，激发情感联结；并基于可持续发展理论，探索虚拟导游、品牌代言等多元商业模式，延长IP生命周期。项目实践为学生提供数字IP构建逻辑、科技赋能文化传承的理论认知、分析数字人创新实践能力及文化自信与科技向善的价值观引导，为文旅行业数字化转型提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The advent of artificial intelligence and the explosion of the metaverse concept have made virtual digital humans an important driving force and key catalyst for future communication. This case study takes the “Liu Sanjie Digital Human” created by the Guangxi Department of Culture and Tourism and the Tourism Development Group as an example to explore the digital transformation path of integrating traditional culture with technology. The project uses virtual digital human technology to reimagine the national-level intangible cultural heritage “Liu Sanjie” and establish a new model for cultural and tourism promotion that integrates intelligent guided tours, cultural explanations, and interactive services. The case study deeply applies digital cultural IP theory, modernizing IP character design and creating a multi-dimensional content ecosystem to enhance the recognizability of cultural symbols; leveraging marketing transformation theory to break away from traditional homogeneous models, it redefines user engagement pathways through 24/7 intelligent services that blend virtual and real worlds, and data-driven personalized recommendations; combining emotional marketing theory, it fosters emotional connections through mountain song cultural resonance and user-created communities; and based on sustainable development theory, the project explores diverse business models such as virtual guides and brand ambassadors to extend the IP lifecycle. The project practice provides students with theoretical understanding of digital IP construction logic, technology-enabled cultural heritage, analytical skills for digital human innovation, and values guidance on cultural confidence and technology for good, offering reference for the digital transformation of the cultural tourism industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《数字营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字文化IP理论；营销变革理论；情感营销理论；可持续发展与拓展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
